General.Name: Eolus Vind AB (publ)
General.Description: Eolus Vind AB (publ) primarily engages in the development, establishment, and operation of facilities for renewable energy and energy storage in Sweden, Norway, Finland, the United States, Poland, and the Baltic states. It operates through Project Development and Asset Management segments. The company engages in the operation of wind turbines; and generation and sale of electricity. It also offers asset management services for facilities for renewable energy. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Hässleholm, Sweden.
